- Created `internal/infrastructure/library/adder.go` with `AddOptions` struct and `AddResource()` function
- Implemented type detection (flag > frontmatter > filename)
- Implemented name detection (flag > frontmatter > filename)
- Implemented description detection (flag > frontmatter)
- Created `DetectPlatform()` and `IsCanonicalFormat()` helper functions
- Created `DetectTypeFromFilename()` for type detection from filenames

**Tasks 2.1-2.4 partially completed**:
